Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.85,0:00:04.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Once again, Millhi accepted my challenge for war.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.68,0:00:07.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be the normal, typical kind of battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.90,0:00:09.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There won't be a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.60,0:00:11.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll definitely protect my people
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.65,0:00:15.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and everyone's future!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.16,0:00:19.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it, Granveil! Lend me your power!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.44,0:02:12.94,Title,Ep Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6\fad(600,0)\pos(440,353)\fs34}  「Grana Fortress's Defense Strategy」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.23,0:02:09.39,Next Episode Dialogues,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Princess Leo,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.39,0:02:15.94,Next Episode Dialogues,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I sincerely apologize. Sister Biore and her soldiers have failed their mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.94,0:02:21.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems they're being held captive at the Fortress of Sreize right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.19,0:02:24.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Then where's Gaul?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.99,0:02:30.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,According to your orders, he is at the Fortress of Sreize, together with General Godwin and Genoise.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.46,0:02:38.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But it seems that Prince Gaul and the others are not very enthusiastic about this battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.89,0:02:40.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.50,0:02:44.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So long as they're able to enjoy it to the fullest \Nwith the people and the soldiers, it's good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.72,0:02:48.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll win this alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.30,0:02:58.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't a motive for this battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.65,0:03:03.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but we've been ordered to attack \Nthe fortress and fight the good fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.37,0:03:04.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.45,0:03:09.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Godwin, sorry to involve you in such a boring task.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.41,0:03:15.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. I've nothing to complain about, so long as I get to follow your Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.70,0:03:16.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.19,0:03:18.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Prince Gaul.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.72,0:03:24.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,According to reports from the previous team, Princess Millhi isn't at the Fortress of Sreize.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.51,0:03:28.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good. Then I'll be more at ease when taking the fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.68,0:03:32.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If we shy away from this battle, it'll stain our honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.81,0:03:36.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's fight our best and give them a flashy show!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.87,0:03:38.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.07,0:03:44.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the wetland area of Chapel Hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.20,0:03:47.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thirty thousand people are finally going to decide their fate here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.88,0:03:53.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The ratio on the battlefield is 5100 to 4900.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.19,0:03:55.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's about numbers, Biscotti's winning!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.25,0:03:58.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's still too early to judge!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.42,0:04:01.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the route to the Fortress of Grana!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.47,0:04:06.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Biscotti's Team Two has just entered the\Narea surrounding the Fortress of Grana!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.80,0:04:11.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Their light infantry is moving forward with shocking speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.92,0:04:22.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! As soon as we cut across this bridge, we'll arrive at their base camp!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.84,0:04:23.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me your best shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.73,0:04:27.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.32,0:04:33.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Spring Plow! Ream Cultivation Beam!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.24,0:04:47.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! It's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.02,0:04:50.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're retreating! Retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.39,0:04:56.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady d'Arquien!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.94,0:05:00.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Leader of the Knights has given orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.40,0:05:01.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.64,0:05:05.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He requests that Lady d'Arquien and Panettone's Team Three
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.78,0:05:08.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,move forward to assist Team Two at the front.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.78,0:05:11.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, many thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.37,0:05:16.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy lines are stretched thin everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.14,0:05:18.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We should be able to quickly cut across them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.15,0:05:23.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukikaze and Biscotti's Team Three, follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.74,0:05:26.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll cut across enemy lines and back up Team Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.51,0:05:27.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.30,0:05:29.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, looks like the situation has changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.67,0:05:33.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady d'Arquien's Team Three is attacking in this area!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.10,0:05:38.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who will win? Princess Leo's lines or\Nthe attacking backup troops of Team Two?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.28,0:05:40.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this is surprising!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.19,0:05:47.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop right there, Lady d'Arquien!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.04,0:05:50.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while, General Bernard!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.99,0:05:52.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.89,0:05:56.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but I won't let you pass through here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.23,0:06:01.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How does a one-on-one battle here sound to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.16,0:06:04.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm not impolite in doing so, I accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.85,0:06:08.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.36,0:06:14.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Bernard, if it's one-on-one, then I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.56,0:06:15.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Laurent?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.86,0:06:17.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Martinozzi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.31,0:06:20.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! It's one surprise after another!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.59,0:06:22.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Will this be a battle between commanders?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.54,0:06:25.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A battle between the leaders of \Nthe knights from both countries?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.36,0:06:30.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I'll take it from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.68,0:06:32.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Move ahead, Lady d'Arquien!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.45,0:06:35.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, many thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.41,0:06:37.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Team Three, let's get moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.99,0:06:38.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.06,0:06:44.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh man, I wonder how many years it's been since our last duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.71,0:06:48.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This will be the first time since we became the leaders of the knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.50,0:06:51.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So it was over three years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.55,0:06:54.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Both of them were born into knight families,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.86,0:07:00.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and, in their private lives, they're friends that send seasonal gifts to each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.43,0:07:01.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They are the generals of both countries!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.90,0:07:05.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the cerkles that they ride come from famous breeds!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.03,0:07:08.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, they both carry spear and shield weapons!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.82,0:07:12.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, generals! Will you battle for your honor?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.23,0:07:23.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It has begun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.96,0:07:26.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Fortress of Sreize!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.88,0:07:31.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Prince Gaul and the Imperial Guards are attacking vigorously!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.27,0:07:40.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tusk Claw Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.97,0:07:57.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Arrow Team, fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.51,0:08:07.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.17,0:08:17.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy's right wing defense has been destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.34,0:08:18.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,General, it's up to you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.43,0:08:28.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A disadvantage in numbers doesn't affect him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.77,0:08:33.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Biscotti's central gatekeepers are flying through the air like leaves and flowers!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.59,0:08:46.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it, Chief? Will it do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.83,0:08:51.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup! The wind came just in time!\NWe should be able to fly through instantly!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.11,0:08:57.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Haran, let's fly to the princess's side right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.72,0:09:03.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ricotta Elmar, riding Haran, the master of the artillery division!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.07,0:09:11.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's sortie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.07,0:09:20.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.84,0:09:26.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.62,0:09:28.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two... go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.64,0:09:47.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Success!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.99,0:09:49.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Vert, in front of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.97,0:09:50.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.77,0:10:12.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Genoise Arrow Team, destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.99,0:10:16.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Our Chief's precious sacrifice did not go in vain!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.54,0:10:28.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for saving me, Haran.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.07,0:10:35.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Let's keep this up and reach the princess and Sir Hero at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.69,0:10:39.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But before that, where can I put on some clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.06,0:10:44.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we are at the the Fortress of Grana!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.88,0:10:49.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Biscotti's Team Two is finally about to enter the fortress gatekeepers' attack range!{"fortress" is an adjective here and doesn't need an apostrophe; apostrophe after s for plural "gatekeepers" is correct}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.66,0:10:56.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,According to Princess Leo's strategy, a special force was picked to protect the base camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.41,0:10:58.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A special force?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.49,0:11:00.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess, stay in the middle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.86,0:11:02.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.56,0:11:05.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're approaching the first defense line!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.43,0:11:08.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Use a protective formation! Spread out and move forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.91,0:11:10.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Defend the princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.16,0:11:11.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.44,0:11:16.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Artillery team, weapons team, take your stance!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.40,0:11:21.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Guns? Cannons?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.43,0:11:26.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hero, are you still able to perform the \Ncrest power that I taught you previously?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.26,0:11:27.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Previously? Which one?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.87,0:11:29.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The firing time or the shield time?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.07,0:11:34.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The shield! You defend, and I'll charge forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.31,0:11:35.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.57,0:11:38.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shield, prevail!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.04,0:11:42.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.04,0:11:52.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Artillery team, shoot the hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.35,0:11:53.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.89,0:11:57.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.72,0:12:15.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.46,0:12:19.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hero Sink has deflected the artillery shell!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.05,0:12:21.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How was that, Eclair?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.09,0:12:24.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What a show-off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.99,0:12:26.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But good move!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.39,0:12:34.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Flash Void...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.15,0:12:38.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Grand Beeline!{is there a cooler replacement for "large"?}{yes; other synonyms for large: colossal, immense, massive...}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.11,0:12:52.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Knights, clear out the injured enemies!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.40,0:12:56.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That was awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.14,0:12:58.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hero Sink and the captain of Imperial Guards, Eclair,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.87,0:13:00.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,wiped out the gatekeepers in an instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.88,0:13:02.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They're now entering the fortress!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.76,0:13:05.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But looks like the weather is changing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.93,0:13:09.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dark clouds seem to be gathering in the eastern sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.56,0:13:39.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was supposed to be a day without stars, yet I received a disturbing image.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.08,0:13:42.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is the battlefield in this fortress?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.21,0:13:52.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't cry. Please don't cry, Millhi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.83,0:13:57.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Things that make you upset, and things that make you feel pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.75,0:14:33.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My Lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.64,0:14:36.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Please lead us to the direction of the fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.58,0:14:41.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm. Lady d'Arquien, Chief Panettone,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.55,0:14:43.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,what is this sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.28,0:14:47.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, it's something like an alarm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.74,0:14:53.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There is danger that will make the normal soldiers unable to enjoy this war.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.07,0:14:56.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll move forward to get rid of whatever danger exists first.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.10,0:14:58.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave the commanding and directing to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.94,0:14:59.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.06,0:15:07.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Could this fluctuation be from a demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.21,0:15:09.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Demons bring disaster to Flonyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.75,0:15:14.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes they burn down an entire country,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.17,0:15:22.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and sometimes they even kill gods. What sinister creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.35,0:15:44.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm tired of waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.33,0:15:47.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be the hero and the ear-drooping doggie?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.93,0:15:57.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now I'm at this castle's \Nhighest point, the Sky Battle Stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.25,0:16:03.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to reward you for coming all \Nthis way, I'll give you a chance to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.45,0:16:11.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Granveil and Ex Machina are both here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.55,0:16:17.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're able to get them, it'll be easier for you to win judging from the scores.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.37,0:16:21.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I won't fight each of you one by one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.00,0:16:25.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't be a problem for the both of \Nyou to come together, so just bring it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.25,0:16:29.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll defeat all of you and take Palladion,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.63,0:16:33.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and then I'll annihilate Millhi's team.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.41,0:16:37.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come, climb up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.45,0:16:47.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Leo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.69,0:16:49.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, there won't be a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.94,0:16:55.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I wait here, the confused hero and that\Near-drooping doggie will bring the Palladion to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.41,0:16:59.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The stars will probably change by then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.66,0:17:00.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.55,0:17:12.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, during this country's great war, I don't like this sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.26,0:17:26.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to intrude, Princess Leonmitchelli.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.39,0:17:34.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If Princess Leo intends to incite war by betting our country's Holy Swords,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.03,0:17:38.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,then it is a must for me to bring the Holy Sword here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.28,0:17:42.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon my impoliteness for doing this on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.52,0:17:48.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible! Why? Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.94,0:17:52.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Leonmitchelli, please tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.67,0:17:59.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell me the true reason behind this war,\Nthe truth that's hiding in your heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.03,0:18:07.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Rouge, Princess Leo and I are...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.31,0:18:09.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can scold me as much as you want later,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.54,0:18:13.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but right now there's no time to explain!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.32,0:18:19.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So long as I snatch this...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.70,0:18:46.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you need the Holy Swords, I'll lend them to you as long as you explain your situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.03,0:18:53.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But why didn't you tell me anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.86,0:19:01.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}We used to be so close.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.14,0:19:04.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You always cared for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.52,0:19:07.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't just about the Holy Swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.66,0:19:10.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All the recent wars,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.58,0:19:16.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Leo, do you... do you really hate me that much?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.27,0:19:18.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.45,0:19:33.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Hero. You look pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.06,0:19:35.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right back at you. Your tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.49,0:19:41.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! That's because the princess insisted on going alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.87,0:19:44.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't disobey her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.70,0:19:48.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, somehow, I have a bad feeling about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.79,0:19:53.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what, we can't move the elevator from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.11,0:19:55.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I confirmed it just now. It's locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.23,0:20:00.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eclair, over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.34,0:20:06.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like... we can climb up from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.76,0:20:08.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.35,0:20:11.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But Hero, the princess is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.40,0:20:13.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, what the princess said was...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.75,0:20:20.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me proceed by myself from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.09,0:20:27.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's fine to go up from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.58,0:20:29.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How old are you? {lit. Are you a kid?}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.58,0:20:32.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have a problem with that, don't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.15,0:20:34.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll even go on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.15,0:20:38.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who says I'm not going?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.68,0:20:46.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're now announcing this to all who are\Nparticipating in the defense of the Fortress of Grana.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.09,0:20:52.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Due to the interruption by storm clouds, the Flonyard Power is weakening.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.29,0:20:59.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Since we can also foresee danger from \Nlightning strikes, please stop fighting for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.39,0:21:00.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I repeat,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.94,0:21:05.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,please put the fight on hold. Move to a safe zone...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.30,0:21:09.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, please move to a nearby shelter on that side.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.13,0:21:22.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eclair!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.83,0:21:30.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Millhi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.22,0:21:31.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Leo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.85,0:21:37.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Leo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.81,0:21:39.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Millhi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.86,0:21:42.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What on earth?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.22,0:21:46.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Sky Battle Stage on the Fortress of Grana has begun to rise!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.36,0:21:48.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! L-L-Look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.41,0:23:52.19,Next Episode Dialogues,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.19,0:23:53.65,Next Episode Dialogues,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hey, Hero...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.65,0:23:54.70,Next Episode Dialogues,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Let's do it, Bernard!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.70,0:23:55.66,Next Episode Dialogues,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Right, Laurent!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.66,0:23:57.38,Next Episode Dialogues,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Everyone's trying their best!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.38,0:23:59.60,Next Episode Dialogues,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Please watch us in the next episode too!
